+/**
+ * Copy a contiguous byte range from a system-RAM buffer to the VBE
+ * banked window, switching banks across boundaries as needed.
+ *
+ * Wraps the SDL3-DOS internal BankedDosmemput() primitive. Handles the
+ * common cases: full-frame flush, single-row band, multi-row band that
